  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: '3D Assets:

    

    *Gypsophila Flower*

    

    ''DEMO: Low Poly
    Flower Pack'' from Unity Asset Store by Emilulz.

    

    *Housing Interior*

    

    ''House
    Interior - Free'' from Unity Asset Store by nappin.

    

    ''Free Wood
    Door Pack'' from Unity Asset Store by Biostart.

    

    ''Persiang Carpets
    - URP'' from Unity Asset Store by CGPAL.

    

    ''VINTAGE LIVING ROOM 3D
    GAME PACK'' from Unity Asset Store by ZNS3D.

    

    ''P3D: Indoor Design
    Starter Kit (3D Models Furniture)'' from Unity Asset Store by Phoenix3d Studio.

    

    *Broken
    Heart*

    

    ''Broken Heart Two-Piece Love Heartbreak Symbol'' from https://sketchfab.com/3d-models/broken-heart-two-piece-love-heartbreak-symbol-d53f95a1619f4e3cb0c5b5e2b35b2c00
    by B1Blender.

    

    ''Broken Heart png'' from https://www.pngwing.com/en/free-png-zcvhn.

    

    *Red
    Heart*

    

    ''Heart in Love'' from https://sketchfab.com/3d-models/heart-in-love-f39ce19b92e246268f4c501b72ea7d0e
    by Azamuki.

    

    ''Glossy red heart symbol a 3d render of a shiny heart''
    from https://www.magnific.com/free-psd/glossy-red-heart-symbol-3d-render-shiny-heart_405497124.htm#fromView=keyword&page=1&position=0&uuid=6b0e5c33-ad88-4ba3-bec1-aa948c7573e2&query=Red+heart+png
    by tohamina.

    

    *Envelope*

    

    ''Letter & Envelope Assets''
    from https://sketchfab.com/3d-models/letter-envelope-assets-bb05f9a28e2b455da934a0b2ea2fc444
    by WaajaaH.

    

    Audios:

    

    ''Draft And Wind.Synth 2.Indoor.Resonant(3osc).wav''
    from https://freesound.org/people/newlocknew/sounds/612185/ by newlocknew.

    

    ''Orthodox
    church bell ringing_2.Close(Eq).wav'' from https://freesound.org/people/newlocknew/sounds/592873/
    by newlocknew.

    

    ''Special Sound-Heartbeat 01'' from https://freesound.org/people/miduno/sounds/671258/
    by miduno.

    

    ''11111.wav'' (the girl laugh behind the phone) from
    https://freesound.org/people/Sapereaudio/sounds/457394/ by Sapereaudio.

    

    ''Peter
    Tchaikovsky - The Seasons: October: Autumn Song'' (outro music) from https://www.yourclassical.org/episode/2018/10/09/daily-download-peter-tchaikovsky--the-seasons-october-autumn-song
    by Ilya Rashkovsky.

    

    ''1970 telephone ring 1-4 seconds cycle NL.wav''
    from https://freesound.org/people/klankbeeld/sounds/663840/ by klankbeeld.

    

    ''BakelitePhoneRingSingleMono.wav''
    from https://freesound.org/people/HerbertBoland/sounds/30085/ by HerbertBoland.

    

    ''Stone
    Door opening.wav'' from https://freesound.org/people/jacko4526/sounds/656029/?
    by jacko4526.

    

    ''Mouse Click Sound for Vlogs, Tutorial Videos and
    More'' from https://freesound.org/people/inkedflorist/sounds/710039/ by inkedflorist.

    

    ''Angry
    Door - Wooden Entrance Open Close Slam Hard A.wav'' from https://freesound.org/people/hisoul/sounds/462665/
    by hisoul.

    

    ''Foot steps'' from https://freesound.org/people/sim2710/sounds/262452/
    by sim2710.

    

    ''Clair de Lune (Debussy)'' from https://pixabay.com/de/music/sch%c3%b6ne-st%c3%bccke-clair-de-lune-debussy-496382/
    by KonstantinPazuzuStudio.

    

    The Painting:

    

    ''kiss'' from
    https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Klimt_-_Der_Kuss.jpeg by Gustav Klimt.












    Narrated
    and Developed by:

    Amirarsalan Sanati

    (https://github.com/Amirarsalan-sn/Will-There-Be-Light)

    [press
    any key to exit]'
